data.description: Spacious six bedroom rambler with a delightful sunroom perfect for enjoying your lovely backyard. This home offers comfortable single level living. Windows and doors have all been updated. The large kitchen has ample counter space and connects seamlessly to the dining room and sunroom. Three season sunroom has ceramic heater with lifetime warranty.  Stunning hardwood floors flow through the main level and its three bedrooms. The main floor bathroom connects to primary bedroom with walk in shower and is handicapped accessible. There is also a washer/dryer hookup in the bathroom, making all living space on one level. Lower level has traditional laundry room, Culligan water softener and water heater is less than two years old. Family room and three more large bedrooms complete the lower level.
